[PHOcr] Empty change for testing on Jenkins97 (10.116.41.97).

Change Details           31/10/2019

NAME
  Project \"PHOcr\"

SUMMARY
  Empty change for testing on Jenkins97 (10.116.41.97).

DESCRIPTION
  What issue?:
    Currently, we usually test for PHOcr on Jenkin (96) on branch master.
    We want to test PHOcr on new Jenkin server 97. But if we use this branch
    gerrit on Jnkin 96 will get the even and testing for it.

  How to fix?:
   On new Jenkin 97, set up new branch for gerrit trigger and create PHOcr change
   then push it to this branch

  What impact by this change?:
     None
  How to test?:
     On new Jenkin 97, set up new branch for gerrit trigger and create PHOcr change
     then push it to this branch

API CHANGE
  None

ARCHITECTURE
  This change must test on platform: linux
